name: STONKS
description: The first revolutionary MEME, inheriting the spirit of GME's resistance, opposes the issuance of virtual currency by rugs and celebrities to harvest retail investors. We have the strongest, most united, purest community of cryptocurrencies, and we are the representatives of decentralization, declaring war on Nasdaq. STONKS is a war against rug pulls, a revolution of collective awakening, an experiment in retail investor unity. It’s not about price, nor market cap. We are creating the “Dumb Money” moment for the crypto industry. We need everyone’s strength.
